message.body: Hey! How are guys doing over there?
We're good! Hunter is napping and HB and I are about to pack up some stuff for tmw!
Oh good. Would you guys be up for some company in a little bit.
Come over whenever!! We are making a veggie lasagna. It will be done at 7 if you want some.
OK thanks I'm making dinner for Logan and I but I'll be over after. I do have to stop at the store to pick up ice cream and bday card so Ill probably get there around 7
